title: You Are Not Damaged Goods | Joel Osteen

description:
No injustice or disappointment can keep you from your destiny. It's time to let go of the past and move into the incredible future God has for you!



Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
